timeline.bodyText:
I think we should not remove this check completely, we allow dynamic view to be in session schema, but not regular views. Right now with the change, regular view will be created successfully using the session schema:
splice> create view session.v1 as select a1 from t1;
0 rows inserted/updated/deleted
ELAPSED TIME = 129 milliseconds
splice> select * from session.v1;
ERROR XJ001: DERBY SQL error: SQLCODE: -1, SQLSTATE: XJ001, SQLERRMC: java.lang.NullPointerExceptionXJ001.U
splice> quit;

